name: Warehouse No. 18
overview:
Warehouse No.18 (Склад № 18) is puzzle game made in Russia by A. Chudov in 1997 for the Dendy system.

The game is a typical Sokoban-type puzzle game. The player moves the warehouse keeper around to sort out the boxes and put them into the slots to complete a round. The player can also customize their own level.
